snippet.title: ASTRO BOT: Rescue Mission | Announcement Trailer | PlayStation VR
snippet.description: ASTRO BOT: Rescue Mission is a brand new Platform game exclusive to PS VR. Take control of ASTRO the captain BOT and go on an epic VR rescue mission to save your fellow Bots who are dispersed all over space.
